title: BRIEF-Sichuan Datong Gas Development to swing to profit in FY 2017

organizations.name: reuters) - sichuan datong gas development co ltd

text:
Jan 30 (Reuters) - Sichuan Datong Gas Development Co Ltd :
* Sees to swing to net profit at 17 million yuan to 25 million yuan in FY 2017 versus net loss at 55.1 million yuan in FY 2016
